Create a custom Lightning Web Component to display Stakeholder records as a related section on the Decision record page.
The component should behave similar to a standard related list but be configurable and reusable across Decision record pages.

Stakeholder records related to the Decision are displayed in a dedicated section on the Decision record page

Component is implemented using a custom LWC

Supports view and add Stakeholder records

Displays key Stakeholder fields (e.g., Name, Role, Contact/Email)

Component is configurable via Lightning App Builder

Follows Salesforce Lightning Design System (SLDS)

Respects user permissions and sharing rules
